game.name: Atlantic City Skyscrapers Racing
game.description: Discover one of the most fun places in the world, Atlantic City, from a different view that you are used to: the skyscrapers. Drive on top of them in every part of the city and try to complete eight amazing levels. Use your nitro power to get some extra speed and do some flips while in the air to get bonus points to your score. Collect tokens and a Poseidon statue to get ahead of the game. Have an incredible time playing Atlantic City Skyscrapers Racing!
